window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Maximus Drago is out searching for supplies for his mother when he ends up in a fight for his life. </b></p> <p>Injured, he ends up saving a legendary creature, then bonds with it. After he heals, he has no idea of what life has for him, but fate has decided on what he has to become.</p> <p><i>This book has harem elements/unconventional relationships, sexual content and cursing. It is intended for mature listeners. The MC ends up being over powered, but who doesn't like a badass, right?</i></p>"; 
